====Verb====
{{en-verb|pan|n|ing}}

# {{transitive}} To [[disparage]]; to [[belittle]]; to [[put down]]; to [[minimize]] the importance of.
#: ''The critics really '''panned''' that movie.''

===Etymology 2===
From a clipped form of [[panorama]].

====Verb====
{{en-verb|pan|n|ing}}

# {{intransitive}} To move a [[movie camera]] [[sideways]].

